<span style="display: block; line-height: 11.3pt; margin-right: 201.35pt; text-align: justify;">**__<span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">Chow</span>__****<span style="font-size: 8.5pt;">, Prof. of Modern Culture and Media at Brown University, </span>****__<span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">in </span>__****__<span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">06 </span>__****<span style="font-size: 8.5pt;">[Rey, The Age of the World Target, pg. 39-41]</span>**</span>

